# Cloudflare Workers AI — Flux-1-schnell for the AI signage mockup.
# Both must be set or /api/mockup returns 503 and the wizard falls back
# to a canvas composite.
#
# Get the account ID from https://dash.cloudflare.com/<ACCOUNT_ID>/...
# Get an API token with the "Workers AI - Read" permission.
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
